    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>basmati rice</strong> and 350ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [700ml]</span><strong> cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
