    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice the <strong>brown&nbsp;onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Top, tail, peel and chop the<strong> carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into matchsticks</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>apple<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
